        "ggIQ9qZTcUv_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0706/4243/4289/files/one-icon.png",
        "ggIQ9qZTcUv_title": "Image Title",
        "ggKaOA1g5xy_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#1F2937;\">Relieves Pressure on Teeth &amp; Joints</span></p>",
        "ggL6PwH_kYp_text": "<p>Calm, science-backed, non-invasive relief</p>",
        "ggMvAYHLtBa_text": "<span style=\"color:#151515;\">How Reviv Helps </span><span style=\"color:#E5C185;\">Reduce Grinding &amp; Clenching</span>",
        "ggNDez-uJSc_text": "<p>Interrupts the neuromuscular patterns that trigger involuntary grinding and clenching episodes.</p>",
        "ggVkQSTUWTs_alt": "Alt Image",
        "ggVkQSTUWTs_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0706/4243/4289/files/2-icon.png",
        "ggVkQSTUWTs_title": "Image Title",
        "gg_RsFeuHfp_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#1F2937;\">Reduces Muscle Overactivity</span></p>",
        "ggkS0HJBIQ0_text": "<p>Chronic jaw muscle tension often radiates to the temples and forehead, causing persistent tension headaches and facial discomfort.</p>",
        "ggpBOQgGn8v_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0706/4243/4289/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_m4aw0qm4aw0qm4aw_1.png",
        "ggpu1MDJD5c_alt": "Alt Image",
        "ggpu1MDJD5c_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0706/4243/4289/files/3-icon.png",
        "ggpu1MDJD5c_title": "Image Title",
        "ggqxZAVDA2Y_text": "<p>Distributes force more evenly, protecting enamel and reducing strain on the TMJ.</p>",
        "ggy1tb5k3NI_text": "<p>Our approach is simple: support natural jaw positioning, reduce muscle overactivity, and relieve pressure on teeth and joints—all while you sleep.</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-607847382289220182"
    },
